# Eye/Retina Transcriber Glasses PCB Layout

## Layers

* Top Layer: Tracks and pads for signal routing
* Bottom Layer: Ground plane and power distribution
* Dimensions: 50mm x 30mm board size
* Component Placement: U1 (ESP32) at center, C1 (Camera) at edge, D1 (Display) on top, B1 (Battery) on bottom

## Tracks

* VCC track: 0.5mm width from B1 to U1, C1, D1
* GND plane: Full bottom layer with vias to top
* Data lines: 0.3mm width for I2C/SPI between U1 and C1/D1

## Vias and Holes

* 10 vias for GND connections
* Mounting holes: 2x 3mm for glasses frame attachment
